{"tid":1319144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚隻便衣俾人圍單嘢重點唔係有冇委任証","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T07:00:05.000Z","uid":29625,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb7637007d46a5344d294325bc88bca76298fff","tid":1319144,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"對圍狗單嘢唔好再講咩無委任証住<br />\n講到無委任証就打咁只會俾人覺得我地狡辯<br />\n<br />\n重點係成件事都係佢自己<span style=\"color: red;\">咎由自取</span><br />\n點解在場咁多差佬，成晚咁多衝突<br />\n得佢一個俾人圍到咁應?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係因為佢離隊衝入人群追打市民激起市民怒火，打到忘晒形落單先俾人以牙還牙</span><br />\n唔通俾佢打到口腫面腫爆晒缸仲要講句thank you sir送佢走?<br />\n有邊個聖人做得到?<br />\n<br />\n[推][Fact checked]被圍狗有片段證明自己離隊追打市民在先<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317644</a>"},{"pid":"89d47503d24b61b00ac6c4c3cf52ab8734c9194f","tid":1319144,"uid":54921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d2a574fed62cbf93d838b33ec0a6d1c8f6c90a","tid":1319144,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a>"},{"pid":"f06dc451352095ec117521d850124b684ef3a5d4","tid":1319144,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"而係佢衝出嚟扑9人"},{"pid":"b1ee2959a18a16f405eb2eb96ab2f236a7b45b05","tid":1319144,"uid":29625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89d47503d24b61b00ac6c4c3cf52ab8734c9194f","tid":1319144,"uid":54921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"文宣一定要離開同溫層<br />\n可以好肯定咁話你聽絕大部分唔知咩事嘅人係唔會理呢啲條文<br />\n呢種講法係說服唔到